 *
 * diff((1-z)^(-1/2)*F(a,-a;1/2;z),z,1)
 *     = poch(1/2-a,1)*poch(1/2+a,n)/poch(1/2,n)*(1-z)^(-3/2)*F(a,-a;3/2;z)
